          <source>Imagine you work for a company that does video data processing and pattern analysis.</source>
        </trans-unit><trans-unit id="102" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>You are building a new prototype platform to process the video from traffic cameras, analyze trends, and provide actionable data for traffic and road improvements.</source>
